g.text: - env determination is based on branch name in which codes are changed
- Netlify put all configuration together in file involving env variable, build and deploy process and so on,
Most other tools separetes and put them in different place
- for sensitive env varialbe setting, have to configure in Netlify UI which like some secret protection tool like vault
- plugins aims to integrate with other services that can be split into two types, one is buildingtime plugin working on build stage
another is runtime plugin working on runtime stage that makes App using third-part services
